If a boolean operation, it evaluated to true. failure - Something went wrong or the boolean operation returned false. 74393f36-b7c1-49c3-892e-4529f9dc34cb.a832565b-1786-456c-b605-2b18d8e39a6d.description=Performs a statistical operation on the given list. Inputs\: list - The list to iterate through. delimiter - A delimiter that separates elements in the list. Returns\: The current element of the list, if the response is has more Responses\: success - the operation completed successfully. failure - failed to process the list or something went wrong. 74393f36-b7c1-49c3-892e-4529f9dc34cb.description=Loops over a specified amount of time and averages a value fed into it over this time. Checks to see if this value is above or below a specified threshold. This flow should only be used as a subflow since using it on its own will always return the continue response unless runLength is assigned a value of 0. When this flow gives the continue response the calling flow must obtain another value, and pass it to this flow again. Inputs\: runLength - The number of seconds this flow should loop. waitTime - The number of seconds this flow should before returning when looping. threshold - A value to compare the averaged value to. VALUE - The value of the most recent function call, which will be added to the average. list - The list of values that will be used for finding the average. timeStarted - Time at which the flow is started. Responses\: less than - The average was less than the threshold. equal - the average was the same as the threshold. greater than - the average was greater than the threshold. Continue - the specified amount of time has not yet passed, the calling flow should run another operation and pass this flow another value. failure - values in keyName could not be averaged. Extra results\: average - the average value of the list. only a result is the response is success. list - a list that is accumulating values. This is erased when the time runs out. timeStarted - the time since you made the first function call. this is erased when time runs out. 74393f36-b7c1-49c3-892e-4529f9dc34cb.e29ad4ba-6272-449d-8ed5-e542081f102d.transition.description=Value added to list. 74393f36-b7c1-49c3-892e-4529f9dc34cb.e3112305-a25a-42d3-9528-cdf3dc4467d7.transition.description=Go get next value. 74393f36-b7c1-49c3-892e-4529f9dc34cb.ee441085-e331-4145-9be4-668ba13eb2b2.transition.description=average was below threshold. 74393f36-b7c1-49c3-892e-4529f9dc34cb.f1b8facb-2e77-487c-8ea5-ac64c2b51324.transition.description=The specified amount of time has elapsed. 74393f36-b7c1-49c3-892e-4529f9dc34cb.f7cb0dfe-99ef-4f45-8efa-0841c600e6c9.prompt=Enter list\:
